Every folder (especially under /components, /routes, /lib, /api) must have a README.md that is:

Automatically updated by Cursor

Structured consistently

Used as a local specification for the folder

Duplicated to /docs/modules/<folder>.md for long-term tracking

README.md Structure

# <ComponentName | ModuleName>

## 📌 Purpose
Explain what this folder/module does in 1-2 sentences.

## 🧱 Key Files
- `index.tsx`
- `types.ts`
- `helpers.ts`

## 🔄 Data & Behavior
Explain what data flows through and any state, context, or hooks used.

## ⚠️ Notes & ToDo
- [ ] Pending issues or improvements
- [ ] Behavior to confirm with Kip

